	   <tr><td colspan=2>Unfortunately the next few levels are your hell levels. I would recommend Highhold Keep (good till lev 30 or so, and even higher if you kill guards too), Splitpaw with a group or partner, and South Karana around the entrance to Splitpaw. At 34 definitely move to Eastern Wastes and hunt walruses and Ulthorks. Levels 26-34 can be hard on us mages, but just stick with it and 34+ is a walk in the park.<br><br>Good luck!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Baron Reeshan Ragefire, Magus of the 52nd Flame, Drinal<br>Mathurin Kerbouchard, Bard of the 36th Song, Drinal<br>Lenrok Thunderwolf, Warrior of the 37th Circle, Drinal</td></tr>
