	   <tr><td colspan=2>K, here's the scoop. Time was, back in the day, the level of the pet you summoned was random within about a 2 or 3 level variation. However a few patches back the got rid of that because people were just summoning like 15 pets till they got one that conned the way they wanted.<br><br>Now when you summon a pet it will be the highest level it can be within the range, every time. So in other words, if your pets con white, they're gonna keep conning white till you ding next.<br><br>However, enjoy that while it lasts, pretty soon they're gonna start conning dkblue and stay that way.<br><br><br><br><br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, the Mad Mage of Povar, 56th season god rod vending machine, CoHer extrordinare, Leader of Defiant Heroes[tm] and arch nemesis of the evil squirrel empire.<br><br>Hate stick and crown left... then.... SKITTLES!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
