	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just been reading through the posts below, I had no idea specialization in conjuration was important.&nbsp;&nbsp;I think I need to do the Temple of Solosek Ro quest to reset my specialisations.  <br><br>Can anyone tell me if there will be any adverse effects i.e spells hitting for less or fizzles until my specialisation improves again?<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
