	   <tr><td colspan=2>for the level 15-23 ish try leveling in Paludal caverns (caverns you say? yes Virginia, the is a dungeon bonus)<br>For level 23 to 29ish try Marus Seru. Not much loot. Well there are a ton of rockhopper hides but the high end ones. There are also quite a few different words and runes. <br><br>Then for levels 29 - 38(where I am now) try Dawnshroud peaks Stay away from the ents (all of them) otherwise your asking to be Amtrak'd! try to solo the shrooms to the left (pull them with low level bolt-type spell then send pet after them to avoid their 60 DMG attacks. keep you pet burned out and with DS. heal the pet twice. by that time the pet has sufficient aggro, then nuke with your biggun. try to stay high up on the wall other wise you'll find the hidden wolves. Trust me you don't want that! <br><br>Oh and going further to the east (I think it is east anyhow) you'll see a cave system that has EITHER rockhoppers (high end pelt ones) or Sambata tribals... either way, unless you are 50 or higher, stay away. Going ever FURTHER east (toward the zoneline for Maidens eye) you'll run into a patch of level 35 ish Sambata GREAT loot for the soloer they drop bricks of acrylia. One stacks, one doesn't. Summon up a WR bag or two cuz they are very heavy. OH and a few kinds of low/mid level ulaks (polished/heavy) drop from them also (hint give them to your pet and enjoy the stats.)<br><br>Just remember to keep your pet healed and with a DS and burn him out at all times. If you can ask a higher mage to summong you a few muzzles of mardu, I think they add 25% haste to pet! awesome stuff for pet since it's summoned. <br><br>You've probably already learned this but I feel I must say it anyhow... Kei=good VOQ=Even better.<br>Though I've never had Voice Of Quelious cast on me, it's KEI + 1, the next level of clarity-type buff! And try to get a kindly BST to cast his MR buff on you to. I'm pretty sure they stack from the test's I've done. KEI gives 16 per tick and BST MR gives an additional 7 (I think) well either way I hope this helps someone. <br><br><br>On the bertox server? send me a tell i play all the time. Jorelanny's the name. I'll try to answer any questions you might have.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
